headline: U.S. Bank Launches Edward Jones Co-Branded Products, Expanding Reach to Millions of New Customers
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, November 03, 2025--U.S. Bank today announced that its co-branded checking and credit card products, Edward Jones速 Everyday Solutions Powered by U.S. Bank速, are now available to Edward Jones clients through its network of more than 20,000 financial advisors.
